課程概述 Course Description
       加強學生對熱對流現象之瞭解及其相關應用和提昇學生對複雜應用問題之解析技巧與能力To present a comprehensive and rigorous treatment of convection and to prepare the student to effectively use convection in the practice of engineering.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
加強學生對熱對流現象之瞭解相關應用提昇學生對複雜應用問題之解析技巧與能力 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Conservation equations2Boundary layer equations3Dynamic similarity and scaling 4Stoke's first problem5Wedge-flow problem6Forced convection7Free convection8Free-convection boundary layers9Natural convection in enclosures10Thermal instability11Thermal instability12Turbulence13Turbulence14Special heat-transfer problems15Special heat-transfer problems16High-speed flow17Mass transfer18Mass transfer,期末考 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


